{"about_the_game":"<strong>Harmless Lies</strong> is a short but captivating 3D Visual Novel about learning from your mistakes and becoming the best version of yourself.<br><br>You play as <strong>Yui Shiraishi</strong>, a 16-year-old girl who transferred to a new high school in hopes of escaping the cycle of bullying she was stuck in.<br>The headmaster assured you that this would not repeat here... but so many things can go wrong, even on the first day!<br>You can feel everyone's eyes on you, judging your every move. <br>And just when things are finally starting to look up... you meet <i>her</i>.<br><br>Can you clear your name and expose the truth before it's too late?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get to know and befriend a diverse cast of characters.<br></li><li>Explore multiple detailed 3D environments.<br></li><li>Sneak around and cause distractions to avoid tense situations.<br></li><li>Practice with the cheerleaders via a rhythm minigame.<br></li><li>Try your best to resolve any conflicts and keep everyone happy.<br></li><li>Make the right choices to unlock one of four endings.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Everyone's Friend!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3005250/b3d25f89164be5bd49d17cc83c13dd4921f18529.jpg"},{"name":"Newcomer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3005250/c3ac55d44e8efaa13a1f5a330fa45a0f7e382329.jpg"},{"name":"After-School Shenanigans","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3005250/fc1f58d10b9d94f7d8ba401e2a4786a11f0c0eca.jpg"},{"name":"Ruined Together","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3005250/3f99304653ca4207740212116573316e4244c37b.jpg"},{"name":"Challenging Perspectives","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3005250/872869a1d782516fc82f0606bc894bf89aa4b66c.jpg"},{"name":"All Paid Of